Changes planned for 0.0.4
=========================

- Remove or replace vectors command
- Replace foreach command with a similar command that does the same but also
  allows to select frame ranges, similar to the select command



Other plans
===========

- Add Sharpening (Unsharp masking, Laplace, ...)
- Add frequency domain manipulations
- Add Segmentation framework
- Add corner detection
- Add Marr/Hildreth edge detection
- Add Hough transforms
- Add Pyramid framework

- Complete the texinfo manual for CVL
